body:
On set 4.30.19

Chris on set of Defending Jacob in Belmont, Massachusetts

“Actor Chris Evans was filming a scene with news reporters on Ivy Road April 30 for Paramount Television’s limited series for Apple TV, ‘Defending Jacob.’ Evans plays the father of a 14-year-old accused of murder. The series is based on New York Times best-seller, ‘Defending Jacob,’ by William Landay.

Captain America actor Chris Evans is bundled up for the cold during a break filming the Apple TV+ series “Defending Jacob’ at 16 Ivy Road in Belmont Tuesday. The series stars Evans, a Sudbury native, and Downton Abby actress Michelle Dockery. [Daily News and Wicked Local Staff Photo/Ken McGagh]”

-via belmont.wickedlocal.com from the morning of April 30, 2019
